{Finkley Down Farm }
Finkley Down Farm was a working farm but now it is a{country park.}People come to visit the farm and there are about a thousand people who come here a month. It has got about 55 different breeds of animals including, foals, calves, kids, piglets, rabbits.
The farm park covers about 30 acres of land.There are about 15 different buildings altogether. Mr and Mrs Waters owns the farm. Finkley Down Farm has got a playground for children. It has a cafe and food for the animals and it has got a gift shop. It has also got a {museum}of farm impliments.
